t failed to start!, Rule.execute called for AdService--stress-1749640247_36:0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman agent is attempting to load multiple times, causing conflicts and failures.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"StressHelper is being used to trigger stress-related rules, leading to high thread activity and potential resource exhaustion.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"calling installed(AdService--stress-1749640247) for helper classorg.chaos_mesh.byteman.helper.StressHelper\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的调用链数据，我已经完成了对故障时间段 2025-06-11T11:10:46Z 到 2025-06-11T11:23:46Z 的初始扫描分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\", \n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend调用AdService的延迟从正常5.5秒激增至54-61秒，延迟倍数超过10倍，出现26次异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService相关调用延迟显著增加：GetCart从3.9秒增至14-26秒，AddItem从5.4秒增至64秒\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"Redis操作HGET/HMSET延迟从1.5-1.7秒增至7.7-29秒，延迟倍数最高达17倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PlaceOrder操作延迟从148秒增至331秒，CheckoutService内部调用CartService延迟从8.7秒增至138秒\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n\n1. **AdService是主要瓶颈**：三个frontend实例调用AdService都出现严重延迟，延迟倍数超过10倍，这是最显著的异常。\n\n2. **Redis性能问题**：CartService依赖的Redis出现严重延迟，HGET/HMSET操作延迟激增，这直接影响了CartService的性能。\n\n3. **Checkout流程受阻**：PlaceOrder操作延迟翻倍，且CheckoutService内部调用CartService出现严重延迟。\n\n4. **级联影响明显**：Redis性能问题导致CartService异常，进而影响CheckoutService，最终影响整个下单流程。\n\n建议下一步深入分析Redis和AdService的具体性能指标，确定是资源瓶颈还是服务内部问题。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的指标数据，我现在处于初始扫描阶段，将对故障时间段内的异常指标进行全面分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"memory_usage\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-pd\",\n      \"reason\": \"内存使用率显著增加，memory_usage从153MB增长到194MB，增长比例23.65%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-pd的memory_usage指标：正常中位数153,415,680字节，故障中位数194,564,096字节，变化率0.2365\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"CPU使用率异常飙升，pod_cpu_usage从0.01增长到0.6，同时rrt和rrt_max显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"adservice-0的pod_cpu_usage变化率193.44%，rrt从3073ms增长到21377ms(增长149.72%)，rrt_max从42983ms增长到197984ms(增长128.65%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"CPU使用率异常，pod_cpu_usage从0增长到0.6，rrt和rrt_max指标异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"adservice-1的pod_cpu_usage变化率200%，rrt从5915ms增长到12636ms(增长72.46%)，rrt_max从42723ms增长到94595ms(增长75.55%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"CPU使用率异常，pod_cpu_usage从0增长到0.6，rrt和rrt_max指标异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"adservice-2的pod_cpu_usage变化率200%，rrt从5873ms增长到13343ms(增长77.75%)，rrt_max从42682ms增长到96255ms(增长77.12%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"最大响应时间显著增加，rrt_max从14655ms增长到16500ms，p99变化率高达163.59%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-0的rrt_max中位数增长11.84%，但p99从92023ms飙升到918971ms，表明存在严重性能问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"响应时间异常，rrt_max从289270ms增长到390919ms，p99变化率104.65%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-1的rrt_max中位数增长29.89%，p99从436195ms增长到1393728ms，表明前端服务响应延迟严重\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **数据库层面问题**：TiDB-PD组件内存使用率异常增长23.65%，可能影响数据库性能\n\n2. **adservice服务全面异常**：所有三个adservice实例都出现CPU使用率飙升和